<plot>A humorous look at a man who yearns to be forgiven for acting on his seemingly natural and, dare we say, God-given desires. But therein lies the question. Is our innate sex drive evil or simply the way God made us? Should we be ashamed of ourselves if we indulge our sexual desires or is church doctrine responsible for centuries of sexual repression and the deviant behavior that must naturally follow?</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?268870</url></doc>
